it</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-BasicDisorder.html#BasicDisorder-mb_bechterew\">mb_bechterew</a></td><td>Mb. Bechterew</td><td>Mb. Bechterew</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-BasicDisorder.html#BasicDisorder-other_arthritis\">other_arthritis</a></td><td>Anden artrit</td><td>Anden artrit</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-BasicDisorder.html#BasicDisorder-congenital\">congenital</a></td><td>Kongenit hofteluksation</td><td>Kongenit hofteluksation</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-BasicDisorder.html#BasicDisorder-mb_calve_legg_perthes\">mb_calve_legg_perthes</a></td><td>Mb. Calvé-Legg-Perthes</td><td>Mb. Calvé-Legg-Perthes</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-BasicDisorder.html#BasicDisorder-epiphysiolysis\">epiphysiolysis</a></td><td>Epifysiolyse</td><td>Epifysiolyse</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-BasicDisorder.html#BasicDisorder-acetabulum_dysplasia\">acetabulum_dysplasia</a></td><td>Acetabulumdysplasi</td><td>Acetabulumdysplasi</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-BasicDisorder.html#BasicDisorder-primary_tumor\">primary_tumor</a></td><td>Primær tumor</td><td>Primær tumor</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-BasicDisorder.html#BasicDisorder-metastases\">metastases</a></td><td>Metastaser</td><td>Metastaser</td></tr></table></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"CodeSystem-GenericValues.html\"><code>https://kip.rkkp.dk/fhir/CodeSystem/GenericValues</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version ?2.23.1</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-GenericValues.html#GenericValues-other\">other</a></td><td>Andet</td><td>Other - used to choose unspecific value not in a valueset</td></tr></table></li></ul></div>"
